reviewText: Blu Ray was very good . Great concert.
Great concert at MSG! Neil and his band are at their best. I first purchased this on regular DVD but soon realized that I made a mistake and then purchased it on Bluray.
This video was great.  The sound and the picture was better than I ever could have imagined. We are Neil Diamond's biggest fans and was happy to  get such a wonderful video of his most popular songs.
The package contained only one of two discs.

Outstanding product and service
